headline: Q4 Discount Retailer Earnings: Five Below (NASDAQ:FIVE) Earns Top Marks
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how discount retailer stocks fared in Q4, starting with Five Below (NASDAQ:FIVE).
